@startuml
title Upper Confidence Bound (UCB) Exploration Strategy

class UCBAgent {
  +actions: List<Action>
  +totalSteps: int
  +selectAction(): Action
}

class Action {
  <<data>>
  +actionType: String
  +estimatedValue: float
  +selectionCount: int
}

class UCBSelector {
  +computeUCB(action: Action, totalSteps: int): float
  +selectHighestUCB(actions: List<Action>, totalSteps: int): Action
}

' Relationships
UCBAgent --> UCBSelector : uses (Selects based on UCB Score)

note right of UCBAgent
  1. For each action:
     - Compute UCB Score
  2. Select action with highest UCB
end note

@enduml
